{"tid":1166980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 多蒙特官宣簽入夏薩特","createTime":"2019-05-22T19:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T00:51:46.000Z","uid":223525,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46e9694d223437923553ad8f4817425ea9824dfd","tid":1166980,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"多蒙特完成了與慕遜加柏翼鋒索爾根&middot;夏薩特（T.Hazard）的簽約。<br />\n       在效力慕遜加柏五年後，比利時國腳與德甲亞軍多蒙特簽下了一份為期五年的合約。在德國左閘舒爾茨週二完成了從賀芬咸轉會後，他成為了多蒙特今夏簽下的第二名球員。<br />\n       「我們很高興索爾根決定加盟多蒙特，」體育總監邁克爾&middot;佐爾克在一份聲明中說：「他是一名經驗豐富的德甲球員和比利時國家隊球員，他將利用他的速度赫射門質量幫助我們提高。」<br />\n<br />\nFrom:新浪足球"},{"pid":"238836bf1ee0eae1804d4037c399dd4af13715be","tid":1166980,"uid":223525,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7351caacbac785ff1835a95c9aac4498e533f3e7","tid":1166980,"uid":61450,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"又係比利時 又係姓夏薩特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪有血緣關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4faeafdeb4b832c3bce7a5755453e890c919e92","tid":1166980,"uid":70754,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"7351caacbac785ff1835a95c9aac4498e533f3e7","tid":1166980,"uid":61450,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"又係比利時 又係姓夏薩特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪有血緣關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:31:15.000Z","msg":"無的，一個老豆係夏雨、一個老豆係夏春秋"},{"pid":"8338ee8d9fc99ef267c